{"tid":2214442,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE 火速在日本回歸！11 月發行新單曲","createTime":"2020-09-23T09:02:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T10:29:38.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5cd9e0d7e969ba07b497a9135caa8e0a9692387a","tid":2214442,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_54e24b539668b2b718feb03b5e76cb87/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-09-23/130309-875635.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_54e24b539668b2b718feb03b5e76cb87%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-09-23%2F130309-875635.png&h=f7c948de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n才剛憑著最新日語精選輯征服 Oricon 單日、單週榜的 TWICE，很快地又要在當地發行新作品了！<br />\n<br />\nJYP Entertainment 今天（23 日）宣布 TWICE 將於 11 月 18 日發行第七張日語單曲〈BETTER〉，並公開了洋溢秋季氣息的四張預告照。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_b734275e7c1936029bfadac3044f3c2a/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-09-23/130309-875637.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_b734275e7c1936029bfadac3044f3c2a%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-09-23%2F130309-875637.jpeg&h=07421847&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_efbdcb1b28680a8ab3d68c9e3237ce50/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-09-23/130309-875639.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_efbdcb1b28680a8ab3d68c9e3237ce50%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-09-23%2F130309-875639.jpeg&h=2624d86d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n處在疫情不穩、諸多活動紛紛取消的時刻，TWICE 的〈BETTER〉以「當下」為主題，將透過這張作品表達「雖然現在很想見面卻見不到，但我們依然相互連結」的概念。搶先釋出的預告畫報，便呈現出每人在日常生活中夢想著重逢之日的模樣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_5aa4236c1507e8cbba9082b4c60cb537/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-09-23/130309-875641.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_5aa4236c1507e8cbba9082b4c60cb537%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-09-23%2F130309-875641.jpeg&h=dfe6e4c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一方面，TWICE 今年 7 月才剛發行上一張單曲〈Fanfare〉，本月則推出第三張精選輯〈#TWICE3〉，兩張作品都分別拿下 Oricon 單週單曲 / 專輯榜冠軍，持續展現她們在當地的高人氣！<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：JYP Entertainment）"},{"pid":"008e4f0946205208e4195a52db0ec074640f20d8","tid":2214442,"uid":368098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:03:03.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383b5466d6a07bf28046246b698b65c8907773d6","tid":2214442,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:05:21.000Z","msg":"我來啦彩瑛"},{"pid":"4eae9916e72c0544f87100f75fc172d9ef5e3c03","tid":2214442,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"383b5466d6a07bf28046246b698b65c8907773d6","tid":2214442,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:05:21.000Z","msg":"我來啦彩瑛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:09:41.000Z","msg":"只有我可以來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.theqoo.net/img/wrvjw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.theqoo.net%2Fimg%2Fwrvjw.jpg&h=36c9f482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/FirmBlissfulAmericancurl-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FFirmBlissfulAmericancurl-size_restricted.gif&h=6ab877f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a85a361b3036cfb45a43424179642632f576e0e5","tid":2214442,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"008e4f0946205208e4195a52db0ec074640f20d8","tid":2214442,"uid":368098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:03:03.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:10:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&amp;fna